cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.IR 

This paper is primarily focused on person re-identification, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques for selecting key persons and improving matching accuracy, which falls under the subcategories of multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses surveillance and security applications, which could be categorized under cryptography and security (cs.CR) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
